---
title: Spiced Beef Burrito Bowls with Guacamole & Mango Bell Pepper Salsa
description: Get ready for this salsa dance! Bell pepper and mango are sautéed with sugar until tender and jammy, then mixed with onion, lime juice, and olive oil for a tangy topper. The fruity garnish is perfectly paired with fluffy jasmine rice, Mexican-spiced pork, and creamy guacamole. Breezy burrito bowls with a tropical twist? Ahh… welcome to (weeknight) paradise.
